      "content": "it's not just being sad. it's the weight of it. i can't go back to being the person i was. everyone thinks im this success, and now i'm just a debt collector's target. i feel like the only way to stop the feeling of being a failure is to just... stop being here. it feels like the only way to protect them from the embarrassment of me.",
